SIGNATURE SEGMENT.

09:48.621 --> 09:49.889
TONIGHT, WE EXAMINE A NEW PLAN

09:49.889 --> 09:50.757
TO DRAMATICALLY REDUCE ONE OF

09:50.757 --> 09:51.825
THE LEADING CAUSES OF DEATH IN

09:51.825 --> 09:52.792
THE U.S., ESPECIALLY AMONG YOUNG

09:52.792 --> 09:54.160
PEOPLE.

09:54.160 --> 09:55.061
WE'RE NOT TALKING ABOUT DRUGS OR

09:55.061 --> 09:56.095
SHOOTINGS, BUT ABOUT TRAFFIC

09:56.095 --> 09:56.729
COLLISIONS.

09:56.729 --> 09:57.430
THEY KILL MORE THAN 33,000

09:57.430 --> 09:58.264
PEOPLE IN THIS COUNTRY EACH

09:58.264 --> 09:59.032
YEAR, INCLUDING MORE THAN 4,700

09:59.032 --> 09:59.833
PEDESTRIANS.

09:59.833 --> 10:00.600
NOW OFFICIALS HERE IN NEW YORK

10:00.600 --> 10:01.501
CITY AND IN SEVERAL OTHER STATES

10:01.501 --> 10:02.368
HAVE BORROWED FROM A PLAN THAT'S

10:02.368 --> 10:03.470
BEEN IN EFFECT IN PARTS OF

10:03.470 --> 10:04.904
EUROPE FOR SOME TIME.

10:04.904 --> 10:05.705
TONIGHT, WE TAKE A LOOK AT THE

10:05.705 --> 10:06.539
COSTS WHEN THE SYSTEM DOESN'T

10:06.539 --> 10:07.373
WORK, AND WHAT'S BEING DONE TO

10:07.373 --> 10:13.413
MAKE OUR STREETS SAFER.

10:13.413 --> 10:15.014
>> Reporter: A REMARKABLE AMOUNT

10:15.014 --> 10:16.182
OF THE TIME, ALL THESE BUSES AND

10:16.182 --> 10:17.784
TAXIS, CARS AND BICYCLES,

10:17.784 --> 10:20.520
JOGGERS AND WALKERS, MANAGE TO

10:20.520 --> 10:22.388
COEXIST ON THE STREETS OF NEW

10:22.388 --> 10:24.924
YORK, BUT WHEN SOMETHING GOES

10:24.924 --> 10:26.759
WRONG, IT CAN BE HORRIBLE.

10:26.759 --> 10:27.760
LEAVING FAMILIES DEVASTATED.

10:27.760 --> 10:28.495
LISTEN TO WHAT HAPPENED IN FRONT

10:28.495 --> 10:29.295
OF DANA LERNER'S HOME LAST

10:29.295 --> 10:32.165
JANUARY.

10:32.165 --> 10:34.033
>> I GOT A CALL FROM OUR

10:34.033 --> 10:35.635
DOORMAN.

10:35.635 --> 10:37.103
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT THE HELL I

10:37.103 --> 10:38.438
WAS GONNA FIND.

10:38.438 --> 10:40.406
SO I RAN DOWN THERE.

10:40.406 --> 10:41.941
AND I SAW MY HUSBAND, YOU KNOW,

10:41.941 --> 10:43.776
JUST SCREAMING, LYING IN THE--

10:43.776 --> 10:46.079
LYING IN THE ROAD.

10:46.079 --> 10:49.048
BUT HE WAS-- I COULD SEE HE

10:49.048 --> 10:50.650
WASN'T HORRIBLY HURT.

10:50.650 --> 10:52.418
AND I LOOKED OVER AND MY SON

10:52.418 --> 10:53.653
WAS, YOU KNOW, LYING THERE.

10:53.653 --> 10:55.121
>> Reporter: LERNER'S NINE-YEAR-

10:55.121 --> 10:55.889
OLD SON COOPER HAD BEEN WALKING

10:55.889 --> 10:56.623
ACROSS THE STREET, HAND-IN-HAND

10:56.623 --> 10:57.323
WITH HIS FATHER.

10:57.323 --> 10:58.191
THEY WERE IN THE CROSSWALK WITH

10:58.191 --> 10:58.992
THE LIGHT ON THEIR SIDE, WHEN A

10:58.992 --> 10:59.792
CAB TURNING LEFT HIT HER HUSBAND

10:59.792 --> 11:00.527
AND THEIR SON.

11:00.527 --> 11:01.394
>> HE WAS LYING COMPLETELY

11:01.394 --> 11:02.128
STILL.

11:02.128 --> 11:02.929
THERE WAS BLOOD COMING OF HIS

11:02.929 --> 11:05.098
EARS.

11:05.098 --> 11:09.502
AND I'M A REAL OPTIMIST.

11:09.502 --> 11:12.705
AND I, KEPT SAYING... AND MY

11:12.705 --> 11:13.773
HUSBAND... KEPT SAYING, "IT'S

11:13.773 --> 11:14.507
BAD.

11:14.507 --> 11:15.174
IT'S BAD.

11:15.174 --> 11:15.942
IT'S BAD.

11:15.942 --> 11:16.776
I WAS LIKE, "NO, HE'S BE OKAY.

11:16.776 --> 11:17.477
WE'LL BE OKAY."

11:17.477 --> 11:18.745
AND, AND HE WASN'T.

11:18.745 --> 11:19.946
MONTHS EARLIER, WHILE RUNNING

11:19.946 --> 11:20.914
FOR MAYOR OF NEW YORK, BILL DE

11:20.914 --> 11:22.015
BLASIO HAD MADE TRAFFIC SAFETY A

11:22.015 --> 11:22.982
TOP PRIORITY.

11:22.982 --> 11:24.017
JUST WEEKS AFTER BEING

11:24.017 --> 11:25.218
INAUGURATED AND FOLLOWING THE

11:25.218 --> 11:26.553
DEATHS OF SEVERAL PEDESTRIANS,

11:26.553 --> 11:27.620
INCLUDING COOPER, THE MAYOR, A

11:27.620 --> 11:28.521
FATHER OF TWO HIMSELF, LAUNCHED

11:28.521 --> 11:29.556
WHAT WAS KNOWN AS VISION ZERO AT

11:29.556 --> 11:30.456
A PRESS CONFERENCE SURROUNDED BY

11:30.456 --> 11:31.824
PARENTS WHO HAD LOST LOVED ONES

11:31.824 --> 11:32.992
TO TRAFFIC COLLISIONS.

11:32.992 --> 11:35.995
>> WHEN I READ ABOUT THESE

11:35.995 --> 11:38.831
HORRIBLE MOMENTS, WHEN I READ

11:38.831 --> 11:41.568
ABOUT THESE TRAGEDIES, AND THIS

11:41.568 --> 11:46.339
LOSS OF LIFE IT'S VERY PERSONAL

11:46.339 --> 11:47.941
FOR ME, BECAUSE I CAN SEE IT

11:47.941 --> 11:48.975
THROUGH THE EYES THROUGH MY

11:48.975 --> 11:51.077
FELLOW PARENTS.

11:51.077 --> 11:52.345
AND OF COURSE EVERY ONE OF US

11:52.345 --> 11:53.713
THINKS WHAT IF THAT WAS MY

11:53.713 --> 11:55.181
CHILD.

11:55.181 --> 11:56.716
AND THE GOAL IS LITERALLY TO

11:56.716 --> 11:57.951
REDUCE FATALITIES ON OUR

11:57.951 --> 11:59.185
ROADWAYS TO ZERO.

11:59.185 --> 12:00.420
>> Reporter: THE MAYOR SAID

12:00.420 --> 12:01.788
ZERO, THAT INCLUDES ALL TRAFFIC

12:01.788 --> 12:03.156
DEATHS.

12:03.156 --> 12:04.223
178 PEDESTRIANS DIED IN THE CITY

12:04.223 --> 12:05.925
LAST YEAR.

12:05.925 --> 12:07.360
NOW GIVEN, NEW YORK CITY STREETS

12:07.360 --> 12:08.561
ARE DRAMATICALLY SAFER THAN THEY

12:08.561 --> 12:09.929
WERE 25-YEARS-AGO, BUT TRAFFIC

12:09.929 --> 12:11.965
FATALITIES, INCLUDING MOTORISTS

12:11.965 --> 12:12.966
AND PEDESTRIANS, HAVE STARTED TO

12:12.966 --> 12:13.800
TICK BACK UP SINCE A LOW IN

12:13.800 --> 12:15.268
2011.

12:15.268 --> 12:16.970
>> SOME PEOPLE HERE THE PHRASE

12:16.970 --> 12:18.404
VISION ZERO AND THEY ASK WHAT'S

12:18.404 --> 12:23.843
REALLY POSSIBLE.

12:23.843 --> 12:25.712
THEY ASK WHETHER THESE ARE NEW

12:25.712 --> 12:27.614
IDEAS, SPECULATIVE IDEAS.

12:27.614 --> 12:28.581
BUT WE WANT TO EMPHASIZE TODAY

12:28.581 --> 12:29.549
IS THAT THESE ARE TRIED AND

12:29.549 --> 12:30.316
TESTED IDEAS.

12:30.316 --> 12:33.019
IDEAS THAT WORK.

12:33.019 --> 12:34.954
THEY HAVE BEEN WORKING IN OTHER

12:34.954 --> 12:37.323
PARTS OF THE COUNTRY, THEY HAVE

12:37.323 --> 12:38.958
BEEN WORKING AROUND THE WORLD.

12:38.958 --> 12:41.995
MOST NOTABLY IN SWEDEN.

12:41.995 --> 12:44.397
>> SO IT'S GOING FROM VERY SAFE

12:44.397 --> 12:46.232
TO SOMETHING MUCH, MUCH SAFER.

12:46.232 --> 12:48.635
>> Reporter: MATS BELIN HELPED

12:48.635 --> 12:50.670
DESIGN THE VISION ZERO APPROACH

12:50.670 --> 12:52.905
IN SWEDEN.

12:52.905 --> 12:54.440
WE CAUGHT UP WITH HIM WHEN HE

12:54.440 --> 12:56.342
WAS IN NEW YORK FOR A SYMPOSIUM

12:56.342 --> 12:58.211
ON THE SWEDISH INNOVATION.

12:58.211 --> 13:00.079
BELIN SAYS THE INITIATIVE STARTS

13:00.079 --> 13:01.981
WITH THE IDEA THAT IT'S NOT

13:01.981 --> 13:04.417
ACCEPTABLE FOR A SINGLE PERSON

13:04.417 --> 13:07.020
TO DIE ON THE ROADS AND THAT

13:07.020 --> 13:10.423
ENGINEERING, NOT ENFORCEMENT, IS

13:10.423 --> 13:13.226
WHERE THE EMPHASIS SHOULD BE.

13:13.226 --> 13:16.796
>> IN VISION ZERO, WE PUT THE

13:16.796 --> 13:19.432
MAJOR... THE... THE FIRST

13:19.432 --> 13:21.401
RESPONSIBILITY ON THE SYSTEM

13:21.401 --> 13:24.937
DESIGNER. AND, OF COURSE... THE

13:24.937 --> 13:26.839
ROAD USERS... STILL HAVE A

13:26.839 --> 13:28.941
RESPONSIBILITY.

13:28.941 --> 13:32.011
BUT IT COME.. GOES BACK TO...

13:32.011 --> 13:40.486
THE SYSTEM DESIGNER.

13:40.486 --> 13:43.122
BELIN POINTS TO THE EXAMPLE OF A

13:43.122 --> 13:44.424
BUSY INTERSECTION WITHOUT A

13:44.424 --> 13:45.758
TRAFFIC LIGHT.

13:45.758 --> 13:46.959
THE TRADITIONAL APPROACH IS TO

13:46.959 --> 13:48.127
PUT ONE UP. BUT BELIN SAYS

13:48.127 --> 13:49.495
THAT'S FLAWED.

13:49.495 --> 13:50.797
COLLISIONS WOULD GO DOWN

13:50.797 --> 13:51.964
DRAMATICALLY, BUT THOSE THAT

13:51.964 --> 13:53.199
STILL OCCUR WOULD LIKELY BE AT

13:53.199 --> 13:54.667
HIGH SPEEDS AND SEVERE.

13:54.667 --> 13:55.802
BELIN SAYS THE BETTER APPROACH

13:55.802 --> 13:56.736
WOULD BE TO CREATE A ROTARY OR

13:56.736 --> 13:57.603
ROUNDABOUT, FORCING DRIVERS TO

13:57.603 --> 13:58.271
SLOW DOWN.

13:58.271 --> 13:59.072
>> THE CRASHES WILL PROBABLY

13:59.072 --> 13:59.706
INCREASE.

13:59.706 --> 14:00.673
BECAUSE IT BE-- BECOME A LITTLE

14:00.673 --> 14:01.774
BIT MORE COMPLICATED FOR-- FOR--

14:01.774 --> 14:02.575
FOR THE TRAFFIC.

14:02.575 --> 14:03.643
BUT THOSE THAT WILL HAPPEN WILL

14:03.643 --> 14:04.343
BE LESS SEVERE.

14:04.343 --> 14:05.178
AND ACTUALLY THE-- THE

14:05.178 --> 14:06.112
ROUNDABOUT MIGHT BE THE

14:06.112 --> 14:07.013
DIFFERENCE BETWEEN LIFE AND

14:07.013 --> 14:07.914
DEATH.

14:07.914 --> 14:09.048
>> Reporter: AS PART OF VISION

14:09.048 --> 14:10.249
ZERO IN SWEDEN, THE COUNTRY

14:10.249 --> 14:11.050
ADDED THOUSANDS OF MILES OF

14:11.050 --> 14:12.218
DIVIDERS, ADDED BREATHALYZERS IN

14:12.218 --> 14:13.586
MANY CARS, AND RUNS ONE OF THE

14:13.586 --> 14:14.687
LARGEST SPEED CAMERA SYSTEMS IN

14:14.687 --> 14:15.855
THE WORLD, NOT TO MAKE MONEY,

14:15.855 --> 14:17.056
BELIN SAYS, BUT TO SLOW DRIVERS

14:17.056 --> 14:18.491
DOWN.

14:18.491 --> 14:19.592
SWEDEN ROLLED OUT ITS VISION IN

14:19.592 --> 14:20.693
1,997 WHEN SEVEN PEOPLE PER

14:20.693 --> 14:21.728
100,000 DIED IN TRAFFIC,

14:21.728 --> 14:23.062
IN TEN YEARS, SWEDEN CUT ITS

14:23.062 --> 14:24.297
RATE IN HALF, AND TODAY THE

14:24.297 --> 14:25.131
UNITED STATE'S RATE IS MORE THAN

14:25.131 --> 14:27.633
THREE TIMES AS HIGH

14:27.633 --> 14:29.135
AND OTHER PEOPLE OUTSIDE NEW

14:29.135 --> 14:32.004
YORK HAVE NOTICED SWEDEN'S

14:32.004 --> 14:33.473
SUCCESS, MINNESOTA, UTAH, AND

14:33.473 --> 14:34.640
WASHINGTON STATE HAVE ALL

14:34.640 --> 14:36.342
IMPLEMENTED VISION ZERO-STYLE

14:36.342 --> 14:38.578
PROGRAMS AND SEEN REDUCTIONS IN

14:38.578 --> 14:41.547
FATALITIES FALL FASTER THAN IN

14:41.547 --> 14:42.715
STATES WITHOUT THEM.

14:42.715 --> 14:44.016
AND MANY OTHER CITIES, INCLUDING

14:44.016 --> 14:45.585
LOS ANGELES, SAN FRANCISCO, AND

14:45.585 --> 14:47.120
CHICAGO, HAVE JOINED NEW YORK IN

14:47.120 --> 14:47.820
RECENTLY IMPLEMENTING VISION

14:47.820 --> 14:52.058
ZERO-STYLE INITIATIVES.

14:52.058 --> 14:53.726
HERE IN NEW YORK, THE PLAN CALLS

14:53.726 --> 14:56.195
FOR INCREASED PUBLIC EDUCATION,

14:56.195 --> 14:57.463
VISION ZERO STREET TEAMS MADE UP

14:57.463 --> 14:58.931
OF POLICE AND TRANSPORTATION

14:58.931 --> 15:07.106
WORKERS HAVE RAISED AWARENESS

15:07.106 --> 15:08.341
HANDING OUT PAMPHLETS AND PSAs

15:08.341 --> 15:09.842
HAVE BEEN PRODUCED ABOUT THE

15:09.842 --> 15:11.577
IMPACT OF RECKLESS DRIVING:

15:11.577 --> 15:13.112
AND LIKE SWEDEN, NEW YORK'S

15:13.112 --> 15:14.113
VISION ZERO CALLED FOR MORE

15:14.113 --> 15:15.281
CHANGES IN INFRASTRUCTURE,

15:15.281 --> 15:16.549
BEYOND THOSE MADE IN THE

15:16.549 --> 15:17.817
PREVIOUS ADMINISTRATION WHICH

15:17.817 --> 15:19.185
HAD ALREADY SEEN DECREASES IN

15:19.185 --> 15:20.620
FATALITIES.

15:20.620 --> 15:21.888
THE CITY HAS PUT ASIDE MORE THAT

15:21.888 --> 15:22.922
$40 MILLION DOLLARS FOR THE PLAN

15:22.922 --> 15:24.457
THIS FISCAL YEAR.

15:24.457 --> 15:25.558
AS PART OF VISION ZERO, THE

15:25.558 --> 15:26.793
DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION

15:26.793 --> 15:27.760
PLEDGED TO MAKE SAFETY

15:27.760 --> 15:28.895
IMPROVEMENTS AT 50 LOCATIONS

15:28.895 --> 15:30.563
EACH YEAR, SOME OF THOSE CHANGES

15:30.563 --> 15:32.098
ARE ALREADY HERE, THE

15:32.098 --> 15:35.067
INTERSECTION WHERE COOPER WAS

15:35.067 --> 15:36.369
STRUCK AND KILLED.

15:36.369 --> 15:37.970
THE DOT INSTALLED PEDESTRIAN

15:37.970 --> 15:39.939
ISLANDS, ADDED TIME TO THE WALK

15:39.939 --> 15:41.174
SIGNALS, AND TOOK OUT THE

15:41.174 --> 15:42.208
PARKING SPACES ON THE CORNER TO

15:42.208 --> 15:44.076
INCREASE VISIBILITY.

15:44.076 --> 15:45.411
THE PLAN ALSO CALLED FOR CHANGES

15:45.411 --> 15:47.113
IN LAWS, INCLUDING ONE THAT

15:47.113 --> 15:48.848
WOULD CHANGE HOW TAXI DRIVERS

15:48.848 --> 15:51.617
WHO KILL OR SERIOUSLY INJURE

15:51.617 --> 15:53.820
SOMEONE ARE TREATED.

15:53.820 --> 15:55.621
LIKE THE ONE THAT STRUCK COOPER.

15:55.621 --> 15:57.557
>> AFTER A FEW DAYS, WHEN I WAS

15:57.557 --> 15:59.625
SORT OF GETTING A LITTLE BIT

15:59.625 --> 16:01.460
MORE, YOU KNOW, SORT OF WITS

16:01.460 --> 16:05.164
ABOUT ME, I THOUGHT, "WHERE'S

16:05.164 --> 16:07.066
THE GUY THAT KILLED HIM?"

16:07.066 --> 16:08.401
"WHAT HAPPENED TO THIS GUY?"

16:08.401 --> 16:10.036
AND THEN I FOUND OUT THAT YOU

16:10.036 --> 16:11.037
CAN KILL SOMEONE IN NEW YORK

16:11.037 --> 16:15.208
CITY AND YOU DON'T GET CHARGED

16:15.208 --> 16:17.243
WITH ANYTHING.

16:17.243 --> 16:19.612
SO IN OTHER WORDS, THIS CAB

16:19.612 --> 16:21.214
DRIVER LITERALLY COULD'VE KILLED

16:21.214 --> 16:23.182
MY SON, STAYED ON HIS SHIFT AND

16:23.182 --> 16:24.283
GONE ON, MADE-- TAKEN ANOTHER

16:24.283 --> 16:25.184
FARE.

16:25.184 --> 16:26.285
>> Sreenivasan: HOW IS THAT

16:26.285 --> 16:27.386
POSSIBLE?

16:27.386 --> 16:28.821
>> IT WAS POSSIBLE THEN BECAUSE

16:28.821 --> 16:30.489
THERE WAS ABSOLUTELY NO LAW THAT

16:30.489 --> 16:32.124
SAID THAT THAT DIDN'T HAVE TO

16:32.124 --> 16:34.126
HAPPEN.

16:34.126 --> 16:35.528
>> Sreenivasan: LERNER AND OTHER

16:35.528 --> 16:36.796
ACTIVISTS HELPED PUSH FOR NEW

16:36.796 --> 16:38.831
YORK CITY TO ADOPT PROPOSED

16:38.831 --> 16:39.999
LEGISLATION.

16:39.999 --> 16:40.967
IN APRIL LERNER TESTIFIED BEFORE

16:40.967 --> 16:45.705
THE CITY COUNCIL IN FAVOR OF A

16:45.705 --> 16:46.639
BILL DUBBED COOPER'S LAW.

16:46.639 --> 16:47.473
IT WOULD SUSPEND LICENSES OF

16:47.473 --> 16:49.175
TAXI DRIVERS PENDING AN

16:49.175 --> 16:50.543
INVESTIGATION.

16:50.543 --> 16:51.577
AND LERNER WAS LOOKING ON AS THE

16:51.577 --> 16:52.678
MAYOR SIGNED IT INTO LAW, ALONG

16:52.678 --> 16:55.448
WITH 10 OTHER BILLS RELATED TO

16:55.448 --> 16:56.148
TRAFFIC SAFETY, IN JUNE.

16:56.148 --> 16:56.983
AND JUST THIS MONTH, THE NEWEST

16:56.983 --> 17:02.722
LAW RELATED TO VISION ZERO WENT

17:02.722 --> 17:04.023
INTO EFFECT.

17:04.023 --> 17:05.358
NEW YORK CITY RECENTLY CHANGED

17:05.358 --> 17:08.928
ITS SPEED LIMIT FROM 30 TO 25

17:08.928 --> 17:09.795
MILES PER HOUR UNLESS OTHERWISE

17:09.795 --> 17:10.863
POSTED. THAT MIGHT NOT SEEM LIKE

17:10.863 --> 17:11.831
MUCH, BUT STUDIES SHOW THAT THAT

17:11.831 --> 17:12.765
TINY DECREASE ACTUALLY DOUBLES

17:12.765 --> 17:13.666
THE CHANCE OF SURVIVAL IF A

17:13.666 --> 17:14.967
PEDESTRIAN IS HIT BY A CAR.

17:14.967 --> 17:16.302
BUT ASKING NEW YORKERS TO SLOW

17:16.302 --> 17:17.103
DOWN ISN'T WITHOUT DETRACTORS.

17:17.103 --> 17:18.237
DARKUAH ADIGUN-BOMANI IS A NEW

17:18.237 --> 17:18.938
YORK CITY CAB DRIVER, AS A

17:18.938 --> 17:20.373
MOTHER OF 3 SHE SYMPATHIZES WITH

17:20.373 --> 17:21.507
THE DESIRE FOR SAFE STREETS, BUT

17:21.507 --> 17:22.441
SAYS THAT FOR CAB DRIVERS LIKE

17:22.441 --> 17:23.776
HER, BEING FORCED TO SLOW DOWN

17:23.776 --> 17:24.977
LITERALLY COSTS HER MONEY.

17:24.977 --> 17:26.078
DARKUAH ADIGUN-BOMANI:

17:26.078 --> 17:27.046
THE MORE YOU PICK-UP THE MORE

17:27.046 --> 17:28.881
MONEY YOU MAKE, SO WHEN IT'S

17:28.881 --> 17:29.815
PRETTY BUSY, YOU JUST CAN'T MOVE

17:29.815 --> 17:33.886
WITH A 25 MILES PER HOUR, YOU

17:33.886 --> 17:35.922
JUST CAN'T MOVE.

17:35.922 --> 17:37.023
AND ADIGUN-BOMANI SAYS THAT HER

17:37.023 --> 17:37.924
CUSTOMERS - FAMOUSLY IMPATIENT

17:37.924 --> 17:39.258
NEW YORKERS - WANT HER TO STEP

17:39.258 --> 17:43.529
ON IT.

17:43.529 --> 17:44.297
>> THEY PRETTY MUCH, PICK IT UP,

17:44.297 --> 17:45.131
PICK IT UP BECAUSE, YOU KNOW,

17:45.131 --> 17:46.065
THE CUSTOMERS ARE USED TO, YOU

17:46.065 --> 17:46.999
KNOW, SPEEDING UP, MAKE UP THIS

17:46.999 --> 17:49.035
LIGHT.

17:49.035 --> 17:50.036
>> Sreenivasan: BUT IF SHE DOES,

17:50.036 --> 17:50.970
A LEAD FOOT MIGHT MEAN A BETTER

17:50.970 --> 17:54.340
CHANCE OF GETTING A TICKET.

17:54.340 --> 17:59.979
THAT'S BECAUSE IN NEW YORK,

17:59.979 --> 18:01.480
UNLIKE IN SWEDEN, VISION ZERO

18:01.480 --> 18:02.415
DOES INCLUDE STEPPING UP

18:02.415 --> 18:03.516
ENFORCEMENT, FOR INSTANCE MORE

18:03.516 --> 18:04.684
AGGRESSIVE TICKETING BY POLICE.

18:04.684 --> 18:05.584
THE NUMBER OF TICKETS ISSUED FOR

18:05.584 --> 18:06.352
SPEEDING AND FAILING TO YIELD

18:06.352 --> 18:07.119
THE RIGHT OF WAY TO PEDESTRIANS,

18:07.119 --> 18:07.887
IS UP 50% COMPARED TO LAST YEAR.

18:07.887 --> 18:08.721
IT'S BEEN TEN MONTHS SINCE

18:08.721 --> 18:09.822
COOPER DIED AT THIS INTERSECTION

18:09.822 --> 18:10.990
AND MAYOR DE BLASIO ANNOUNCED

18:10.990 --> 18:12.825
VISION ZERO. FROM JANUARY

18:12.825 --> 18:15.294
THROUGH THE END OF OCTOBER HERE

18:15.294 --> 18:16.762
IN NEW YORK CITY, 209 PEOPLE

18:16.762 --> 18:20.299
HAVE DIED IN TRAFFIC CRASHES,

18:20.299 --> 18:24.570
INCLUDING 101 PEDESTRIANS.

18:24.570 --> 18:26.005
A DECREASE FROM LAST YEAR.

18:26.005 --> 18:26.706
BUT STILL A LONG WAYS FROM

18:26.706 --> 18:28.607
ZERO.

18:37.750 --> 18:38.718
>> Sreenivasan: DO YOU AGREE

18:38.718 --> 18:39.585
WITH THE 'VISION ZERO' APPROACH

18:39.585 --> 18:40.353
TO COMBAT VEHICLE-RELATED

18:40.353 --> 18:41.120
FATALITIES?

